Cell["\<\
In order to check more random results, it is more efficient to first \
calculate the output state right before the measurement.\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->1276748348,ExpressionUUID->"5da8a50a-fa6f-436c-b031-0e93242fb4f7"],

