 FractionBox["3", "8"]], "Output",
 CellLabel->"Out[41]=",
 CellID->717348529,ExpressionUUID->"22f70930-b265-4fff-aa5d-93a28df4edac"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
From the above random result, we determine the period of the function by \
utilizing the continued fraction representation of the estimated phase.\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->209396844,ExpressionUUID->"72215871-ba63-425f-b6c4-5ce3f9dc7119"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[{
 RowBox[{"cnt", "=", 
  RowBox[{"ContinuedFraction", "[", "phi", "]"}]}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
 RowBox[{"candidates", "=", 
  RowBox[{"Convergents", "[", "cnt", "]"}]}]}], "Input",
 CellLabel->"In[42]:=",
 CellID->716244675,ExpressionUUID->"af48abf8-2857-4256-a69e-eac8338cc553"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"{", 
  RowBox[{"0", ",", "2", ",", "1", ",", "2"}], "}"}]], "Output",
 CellLabel->"Out[42]=",
 CellID->503532645,ExpressionUUID->"2853088c-7121-402d-9134-6e069bc3894c"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{"{", 
  RowBox[{"0", ",", 
   FractionBox["1", "2"], ",", 
   FractionBox["1", "3"], ",", 
   FractionBox["3", "8"]}], "}"}]], "Output",
 CellLabel->"Out[43]=",
 CellID->1787595335,ExpressionUUID->"671a715e-d8c4-44a8-8a84-6ad8c4c48c31"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell["\<\
From the above convergents, we have two candidates 3 (and its multiples 6, 9, \
12, 15 are also candidates) and 16. Evaluation of the function for some \
arguments confirms that 3 is the period of the function.\
\>", "TechNoteText",
 CellID->638836156,ExpressionUUID->"28a95976-be8e-44ec-89d8-2ec58c04aecd"]
}, Open  ]],

